=Analyze these AI news items and create a digest WITH INSIGHTS:

{{ $json.emails.map((email, i) => `Story ${i+1}:
Title: ${email.subject}
Source: ${email.from}
URL: ${email.mainUrl}
Content: ${email.snippet}`).join('\n\n') }}

For each story, produce:
- A 2-3 sentence plain-English summary
- A "Why This Matters" insight: the strategic implication, not a restatement

Then identify the 1-2 biggest trends across all of today's stories.
Return clean sections with clear headers.

